readable.content: A dog catches a Frisbee at a baseball field during a game . A dog jumps in the air to catch a Frisbee , while many people watch . A person in shorts is holding a Frisbee while team member in red shirts and spectators look on . A woman is using Frisbees to play with a dog in front of a stadium crowd and a group of baseball players . Woman and dog do Frisbee tricks as crowd watches in baseball stadium .
